We would like to book a table for:
<br/>
<% @venue_bookings.each_with_index do |venue_booking, index| %>
<% venue_booking_mailer_presenter = VenueBookingMailerPresenter.new(venue_booking) %>
<%= content_tag :strong, "GROUVLY CREW ##{(index + 1)}", style: 'text-decoration: underline' if @is_multiple_table_booking %>
<%= render partial: 'pools_matched_mailer/reservation_details', locals: {
                                                                  participents_count: venue_booking_mailer_presenter.participents_count,
                                                                  booking_date: venue_booking_mailer_presenter.booking_date,
                                                                  booking_time:  venue_booking_mailer_presenter.booking_time,
                                                                  first_reservation_name: venue_booking_mailer_presenter.first_reservation_name,
                                                                  second_reservation_name: venue_booking_mailer_presenter.second_reservation_name
                                                              } %>
<% end %>
Please confirm the booking by clicking OK below or NO if you don’t have availability for that date and time.
<br/>
<br/>
<%= link_to 'OK', venue_confirm_booking_url(booking: @venue_bookings_slugs, protocol: 'https'), { style: @venue_booking_mailer_presenter.style_yes_button } %>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<%= link_to 'No', venue_reject_booking_url(booking: @venue_bookings_slugs, protocol: 'https'), { style: @venue_booking_mailer_presenter.style_no_button } %>
<br/>
<br/>
Note: If you need to cancel the booking after you confirmed please email us.
